Package: shinyspring
Title: Build Fast Shiny Applications
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person('Niraj', 'Juneja', email = 'shambhuone12@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: A fast shiny apps development framework with templates based on shinydashboardPlus ,
            admin LTE based bs4Dash.In collaboration with the package sweetmods, shinyframework enables
            you to focus on core app development only.A lot of modules typically needed for a robust application 
            are available to shinyframework in a plug and play manner.
